{"word":"ἀναπλάσσω","slug":"ἀναπλάσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναπλάσσω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to form anew, remodel</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <el>ἀναπλάσασθαι οἰκίην</el> <i>to rebuild one's</i> house, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to invent</i>, in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to plaster up</i>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>κηρὸν ἀναπεπλασμένος</el> <i>having</i> wax <i>plastered</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}